<dl id="n41181a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41181a">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41181a"> 181(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> wuzu ~ </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: <i>Wuzu</i> is the name for the ritual ablution which should precede the act of prayer in Islam. It includes cleaning the teeth and washing the hands, face, forearms and feet with water in a prescribed manner </mm> </dd></dl>
